DESCRIPTION2: 50mm ID, 12mm offset (20mm offset incl. sprocket width). Stock style for all 82-85 FXR 5-speed models. The OEM 12mm built-in offset of the FXR sprocket is a good solution to add 6mm additional clearance for 4-speed custom bikes for extra wide rear tires. The FXR type sprocket is otherwise identical to the commonly used FL, FX rear sprockets, which have just 6mm offset.
description_long: 50mm ID, 12mm offset (20mm offset incl. sprocket width). Stock style for all 82-85 FXR 5-speed models. The OEM 12mm built-in offset of the FXR sprocket is a good solution to add 6mm additional clearance for 4-speed custom bikes for extra wide rear tires. The FXR type sprocket is otherwise identical to the commonly used FL, FX rear sprockets, which have just 6mm offset.

DESCRIPTION2: Foam. 9" rider seat width, with a tapered passenger seat. Designed for a custom low look. All seams and edges have been smoothed and the shape is rounded, for a fluid appearance. Manufactured with LePera's 'Marathon' high density foam.

DESCRIPTION: NC Repl. Beaded Heavy Duty™ Windshield - Top window
DESCRIPTION2: Replacement top window for National Cycle's 5-bolt pattern Beaded Heavy Duty™ windshields. This windshield is manufactured from FRM hard coated clear Lexan® polycarbonate which is the highest quality motorcycle windscreen material available. Offers superior optics, scratch-resistance, durability and should not be mistaken with import products.   Overall screen height: 15.38" (39.0cm).   Top of center mount hole to top of screen: 14.88" (37.7cm).   Width: 22.25" (56.6cm).     Note: Will not fit OEM 7-bolt pattern windshields. See 563896 for OEM 7-bolt pattern windshields.
DESCR_TYPE: All H-D with National Cycle 5-bolt Beaded Heavy Duty windshields

Will replace all late model 'round top' top windows. This windshield is manufactured from FRM hard coated clear Lexan® polycarbonate which is the highest quality motorcycle windscreen material available. Offers superior optics, scratch-resistance, durability and should not be mistaken with import products.   Overall screen height: 15.38" (39.0cm).
